00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:27,520
[Yan Zhiming] He's catching up.

274
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,600
It's 95% from the right.

275
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,960
Right side.

276
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,960
[Yan Zhiming grunts]

277
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:36,080
-[gasps]
-[umpire 2] It's 15-30.

278
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:37,720
[Yan Zhiming] Why did it go to the left?

279
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:43,160
Lu Xia is getting faster.

280
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,480
Can Lu Xia also anticipate
the drop points?

281
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:52,160
No, only Yan can do that.

282
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:55,680
I think Lu Xia makes a judgment

283
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,320
before he jumps.

284
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:59,120
He can't do this

285
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,880
without a good grasp of tennis.

286
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:05,640
I guess Zhiming is feeling like
he's playing with someone else now.

287
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:09,280
[tense music]

288
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:11,320
I may not be able to hit the ball

289
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,360
even when I can estimate the drop points.

290
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,840
But...

291
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,480
Hey.

292
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,400
[exhales sharply]

293
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,600
There are cases where

294
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:22,280
you can't hit it back
by just estimating the drop points.

295
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,760
One is the legendary Cool Drive.

296
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,920
The other is what I'm going to do now.

297
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,960
[Yan Zhiming] Why is he changing hands?

298
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,240
What about his right-hand serve?

299
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:41,960
-[thwacks]
-[Lu Xia grunts]

300
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:43,560
[whooshes]

301
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,960
[pants]

302
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,840
Twist Serve is awesome.

303
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,400
Twist Serve?

304
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,960
Who knows that he can do
a right-hand Twist Serve?

305
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,400
Brilliant.

306
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:00,240
Lu Xia is...

307
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,800
an excellent freshman indeed.

308
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:05,880
There will be more unexpected surprises.

309
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,840
[Yan Zhiming] Twist Serve.

310
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:15,200
He is left-handed.

311
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:16,600
How can he have

312
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,920
such a powerful right-hand serve?

313
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,440
Hey, watch your glasses.

314
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:25,520
[tense music]

315
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,160
[Yan Zhiming] I can't lose.

316
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,680
I will get it

317
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:41,960
with accurate data calculation.

318
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:45,040
PHYSICAL, SPEED, TACTICS,
MENTAL, ATTACK, DEFENSE

319
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:52,040
[Yan Zhiming] When dealing
with a Twist Serve,

320
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:54,640
step backward with the left foot,

321
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,680
turn right, and catch it backhand.

322
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:02,640
[Yan Zhiming gasps]

323
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:07,920
My data is useless.

324
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:12,079
The game ends here. It's 7-5. Lu Xia wins.

325
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:14,119
[all cheering]

326
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:18,000
[Peng] Come give me a hug.

327
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:20,880
-[Mu chuckles]
-[Ying and Peng cheering]

328
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:27,079
-[Ying] Whoa!
-[Mu] Yeah!

329
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,760
[Ying and Peng] Lu Xia.

330
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:36,000
You can add that one in your database.

331
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,640
I lost. You are excellent.

332
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,760
It was a good game.

333
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,560
[Lu Xia] Thank you.

334
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,720
[Yan Zhiming] Dealing
with a right-hand Twist Serve,

335
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:50,800
the success rate

336
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:54,040
will increase by 8.35%
with a lifting foot.

337
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:02,040
I will never play with you again.

338
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:08,320
[Coach Qi] Everyone showed great effort

339
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,840
in this qualifying.

340
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:11,800
Now let me announce

341
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:14,080
the list for the first team.

342
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,920
-Mu Siyang.
-Here.

343
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:19,120
-Chi Dayong.
-Here.

344
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:21,320
-Tang Jiale.
-Here.

345
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,800
-He Xinglong.
-Here.

346
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:26,040
-Zhang Baiyang.
-Here.

347
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,880
-[Coach Qi] Zhuo Zhi.
-Here.

348
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,400
-Qiao Chen.
-Here.

349
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:33,920
Lu Xia.

350
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,800
[applause]

351
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,040
Here.

352
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,520
Lu Xia is amazing.

353
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:44,600
When can I be a main player?

354
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,200
Forget about it.

355
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,200
Just continue picking up balls.

356
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:49,640
[Coach Qi] All right.

357
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:52,320
The group match of the municipal contest
is about to start.

358
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:55,040
Everyone, do your best.

359
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,840
Don't make yourselves regret anything.

360
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,920
[all] Yes.

361
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,280
Dismissed.

362
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,720
[Mu] Hey, Lu Xia.

363
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,880
Could you teach me
how to play tennis next week?

364
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:11,000
NO. 199, ZHI CHUN ROAD

365
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,760
[light music]

366
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,040
[Siyang] Yan.

367
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,760
You still have a lot of opportunities.

368
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:27,240
Captain.

369
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:28,800
Are you comforting me?

370
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:32,600
[sighs deeply]

371
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:40,160
We have a different team this year.

372
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,480
You lost to Lu Xia and Baiyang,

373
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:44,680
but that doesn't mean you're incompetent.

374
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,760
Captain, I don't need
your comforting words.

375
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:50,320
I've calculated it.

376
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,560
If Lu Xia and Baiyang enter
the first team,

377
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:56,720
our odds in the regionals
will increase by 3.51%.

378
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:59,120
As long as our team wins,

379
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,800
I will do whatever it takes.

380
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:07,000
Yan, I hope you can help us
achieve a systematic training

381
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,120
with your data analysis.

382
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,240
Please.

383
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:13,680
Mmm.

384
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:21,680
[Yan Zhiming] But...

385
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,320
I will never give up.

386
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:30,680
[school bell chimes]

387
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:32,200
[teacher] The class is over.

388
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:34,560
[student 2] I'm the only one
who can work out

389
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:35,640
that mathematical problem.

390
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:39,520
[Ying] That snail that you drew
is so cute.

391
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:40,480
GO!

392
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:42,200
[Peng] This is a dragon.

393
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:45,360
Our slogan is full of vigor,
just like a dragon.

394
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:50,040
-[Ying] How about this color?
-[Peng] Let's see.

395
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,680
[both laugh]

396
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:01,640
[presenter on TV] The Jiang Nan chefs
were racking their brains for it.

397
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,320
The best achievement is to take oil

398
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:07,920
-from crab paste and crab roe.
-[telephone ringing]

399
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,440
-Hello?
-[Coach Qi] It's me.

400
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,120
Hi, Coach Qi. What's up?

401
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,400
I may not have the time to accept
your dinner invitation.

402
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,360
[laughs]

403
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,440
[Coach Qi] He entered the first team
as a freshman.

404
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:21,320
Just like you did back then.

405
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,280
Oh.

406
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:26,480
-Really?
-[Coach Qi chuckles]

407
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,920
[Coach Qi] Why would I lie to you?

408
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:29,760
[laughs]

409
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:32,600
He is my son.

410
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:35,880
Like father, like son.

411
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,320
[laughs]

412
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:38,520
I...

413
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:39,840
[dial tone beeps]

414
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:47,160
He made it.

415
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,680
We should celebrate it

416
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:53,400
with my elaborately creative
Chinese cuisine.

417
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:03,480
[gasps]
What are you doing here?

418
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:07,120
[Peng] Look at what we made.
Not bad, right?

419
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:11,240
Mm. It's good. Thanks for your hard work.

420
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,840
Mm-hm.

421
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,240
How can we help you?

422
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:19,080
I am looking for Lu Xia.

423
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,960
He had already left.

424
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:23,600
-He left?
-Yes.

425
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:30,480
Please give him this.

426
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:34,360
[gasps]
It's the main players' uniform.

427
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:35,920
[giggles]

428
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:39,760
Okay. But it's Saturday tomorrow.

429
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,400
I might not see him either.

430
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:43,840
[Peng] It's okay.

431
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,280
You can count on us.

432
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:49,400
Mu asked Lu Xia to play tennis tomorrow.
We can give him then.

433
00:22:50,040 --> 00:22:51,240
Thank you.

434
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,760
-Mm.
-Mm.

435
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:55,560
Bye.

436
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:58,480
He seems to be in a hurry.

437
00:22:58,560 --> 00:23:00,720
Maybe we should give it back to Siyang.

438
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:02,600
No.

439
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:06,520
Don't you want to see
Lu Xia putting it on?

440
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:07,760
[soft chuckle]

441
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,880
[Peng] Just listen to me.

442
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:22,200
[Lu Xia] Dad, where are the chairs?

443
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,920
[Xiangqian] It's a hot day.
It's cool to sit on the ground.

444
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:31,000
How's your training?

445
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,000
I have a long way to go.

446
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,960
I know you weren't able

447
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,840
to become a main player.

448
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:42,240
But don't be disappointed.

449
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:44,040
I know you want to enter
the first team soon.

450
00:23:44,520 --> 00:23:48,520
So I made creative Chinese cuisine
especially for you.

451
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,120
It's an Italian Harvest.

452
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,760
[sighs]
This again?

453
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,640
[Lu Xia] You put crayfish on pizza.

454
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:03,920
You ruined both of them.

455
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:08,120
It's your daddy's love for you.

456
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,400
[light music]

457
00:24:15,080 --> 00:24:17,880
I got into the first team today.

458
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:20,520
That's great. Let's celebrate.

459
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:23,480
-Eat.
-I'm not hungry.

460
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,040
[sighs]

461
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:28,520
You don't even know

462
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:33,800
what your grandfather prepared for me
when I became a main player.

463
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:36,200
I'm not interested.

464
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,720
Okay, let me tell you.

465
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:41,760
Your grandfather
didn't like me to play tennis.

466
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:43,560
[Xiangqian]He unplugged the valve
of my bike,

467
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,640
so I had to run eight kilometers
to school every day.

468
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:47,120
[both laughing]

469
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:50,920
[grunts]

470
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:56,560
[Xiangqian] Everybody laughed at me.

471
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,520
-At last, he found such a big...
-Fine. I'll eat.

472
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:11,240
Dad, let's eat together.

473
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:14,160
You're a growing boy.

474
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:18,680
You should eat first. There's more inside.

475
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,000
[comical music]

476
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:31,040
[Ying] Lu Xia is playing tomorrow.

477
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:32,720
I will prepare him some food.

478
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,880
Tomatoes are rich

479
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:43,680
in vitamin C.
[laughs]

480
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,480
Mmm.

481
00:25:54,560 --> 00:25:56,280
A carrot is good

482
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,440
for his vision.

483
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,640
[chuckles]

484
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:07,680
Finally, I should add some corns

485
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:09,800
and mushrooms.

486
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:13,560
Lu Xia is practicing every day.

487
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:16,400
He needs a lot of energy.

488
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,880
[chuckles]

489
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,560
[light music]

490
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,560
[Mu] Not bad, right?

491
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,320
[sighs]

492
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:44,080
Qi Ying and Peng Xiang
nagged me to bring them here.

493
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:45,800
And they're the ones who's late.

494
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:47,000
Let's go first.

495
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:47,920
Where is Qiao Chen?

496
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:50,840
I don't know. They're not punctual.

497
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:53,040
[Mu's father] Hey, come here.

498
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,160
Dad.

499
00:26:58,360 --> 00:26:59,480
He is my classmate.

500
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:00,880
-[Mu's father] Oh. Hello.
-Mm.

501
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:03,120
You can practice here.

502
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:05,280
-Just do not bother the others, okay?
-Okay.

503
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,280
[Mr. Huang] Coach.

504
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:08,680
I've been looking for you.

505
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,840
I'm here for my class.

506
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:12,560
Fine. Uh...

507
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,400
You can go to section three.

508
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:19,440
Section three?
This section is good. Let's practice here.

509
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,960
[Mr. Huang] Take my bag.

510
00:27:21,520 --> 00:27:22,480
Put it in the cabinet.

511
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,400
Be careful. It's new and expensive.

512
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:28,960
Who is he?

513
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:30,720
He is Mr. Huang, our regular customer.

514
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:32,280
He is always like this.

515
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,920
We are used to it.

516
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:36,040
We see people like that everywhere.

517
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:40,320
Dad, we can go to section three.

518
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,560
No, let me talk to him.

519
00:27:43,360 --> 00:27:44,360
Mr. Huang.

520
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:47,040
What's taking you so long?
Put my bag away.

521
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:49,760
You're wasting my time. I paid for this.

522
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:51,600
Be quick.

523
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:55,160
Let's go to section three.
We have to wait for Qiao Chen.

524
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,520
[Qiao Chen] Damn. Damn. Damn.

525
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:05,560
Hello, my dear fans.

526
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:07,320
I just showed you

527
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,160
the inside of my hostel.

528
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:11,360
It's in the new Chinese style.
Simple and comfortable.

529
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:14,360
And it's also quiet outside.

530
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,840
It's a wonderful to live here.

531
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:19,080
And there are almost no cars
on this street.

532
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:22,680
-Don't worry about...
-Excuse me. Excuse me. Excuse me.

533
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,280
Who is this? Damn?

534
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:26,360
[crashes]

535
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:34,240
[panting]

536
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:37,920
Let me get some rest. I'm exhausted.

537
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:43,360
What? You can talk for half a day
but only play for a short while.

538
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:44,720
[panting]
Lu Xia.

539
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,200
There is a pitching machine.

540
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:47,880
Just play by yourself.

541
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:50,640
[Mr. Huang] Do you even know
how to play? Do you?

542
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:53,800
Hey. I won't pay you for this.

543
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,760
You're warming up for 15 minutes?

544
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:58,000
-Is this all you can do?
-[woman 1] What happened?

545
00:28:58,200 --> 00:29:00,840
You will strain your muscles
if you don't warm up.

546
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,360
Look at me.

547
00:29:03,120 --> 00:29:06,240
I was a semi-professional player.

548
00:29:06,320 --> 00:29:09,120
You have to meet my level. Understand?

549
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:12,160
But you will strain your muscles
if you don't warm up.

550
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:15,240
Does your son only warm up in Yu Qing?

551
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:18,000
-You...
-[Mr. Huang] What?

552
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:20,280
-What kind of coach are you?
-[Mu] He's so bossy.

553
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:24,400
[Mr. Huang] You're wasting my 15 minutes.
You have to teach according to the level.

554
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:27,040
You're too slow.

555
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:29,320
I think you should teach an old man.

556
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,040
Why don't you teach Tai Ji?

557
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:32,520
-I'm telling you...
-Sir.

558
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:34,840
Could you teach me how to play tennis?

559
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:36,520
You see?

560
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:38,840
You're finished. Let me be the coach.

561
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,560
You want me to teach you how to play?

562
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,400
Okay.

563
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:44,560
Please show mercy.

564
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,560
[Qiao Chen grunts]
What are you doing?

565
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,440
Don't move.

566
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:54,920
Secure the scene.

567
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,120
What?

568
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:58,120
You're trying to frame me.

569
00:29:58,200 --> 00:30:00,160
What are you talking about?

570
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:02,720
Can't you see how seriously hurt I am?

571
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:06,360
I was shouting at you.

572
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:07,600
But you didn't move at all.

573
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,800
What are you talking about?

574
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:12,000
Look at my cell phone.

575
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:13,760
Shut up and pay for it.

576
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:15,160
You should pay me for my bicycle.

577
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:18,480
Is your bicycle that important, huh?

578
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:19,920
Do you know what's on my phone?

579
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:21,240
Do you know Hua Chenyu?

580
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,520
I kept many of his free lossless
audio codec audio.

581
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:25,440
You will not understand.

582
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:26,480
Sir.

583
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:28,400
I know.

584
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,800
You...

585
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,920
[comical music]

586
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:39,760
[gasps]

587
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,720
[comical music]

588
00:30:59,600 --> 00:31:01,680
-Sir.
-Boy.

589
00:31:03,080 --> 00:31:04,240
You have good taste.

590
00:31:05,320 --> 00:31:07,560
It's a surprise
that you also like his music.

591
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:10,000
I'm really excited.

592
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,760
I would like you to see my collection,
his offprint photos.

593
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:16,280
Does he have a photo album?

594
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,160
[sobs]
I compiled them myself.

595
00:31:19,760 --> 00:31:22,520
-Uncompressed and out of print.
-Really?

596
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:24,040
Come with me.

597
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:25,440
Let me tell you about it.

598
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:26,480
Okay. Okay.

599
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,160
Let's go.

600
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:34,160
[Xiangqian] Every photo is exquisite.

601
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:41,360
[panting]

602
00:31:41,520 --> 00:31:42,520
[Ying gasps]

603
00:31:43,840 --> 00:31:44,840
[Mr. Huang groans]

604
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:50,160
[Mr. Huang] I didn't even
get a single point.

605
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:52,240
Who are you, boy?

606
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:55,440
Listen, he is a freshman main player.

607
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,480
A freshman?

608
00:31:59,120 --> 00:32:01,240
-[Mr. Huang] That's impossible.
-Awesome.

609
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:04,160
You will strain your muscles
if you do not warm up.

610
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:06,400
-Right, sir?
-Yes.

611
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:14,760
-[Mr. Huang] Come on! Come on! Come on!
-[Mu grunting]

612
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:18,560
-[Mr. Huang] Come on!
-Sorry, I brought some snacks.

613
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:20,360
-Let's eat together.
-[Mr. Huang] Come on!

614
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:23,360
-Come on!
-How many did you make?

615
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,120
Just a little.

616
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,120
-Come on! Come on!
-[Mu panting]

617
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:30,280
[Mr. Huang] Good.

618
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,960
Come on!

619
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:36,320
-Come on! Come on!
-Lu Xia.

620
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:37,520
Is it good?

621
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:39,080
It's far from good.

622
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,480
[Mr. Huang] I'll get it.

623
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:43,800
-[both panting]
-[grunts]

624
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:45,400
He plays really bad.

625
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:50,080
-[Mr. Huang] Come on! Come on! Come on!
-Ying is asking you if this tastes good.

626
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:53,120
-Come on! Come on! Come on!
-Yes.

627
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:58,840
[Mr. Huang] Come on! Come on! Come on!

628
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,000
[soft chuckle]

629
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:07,040
[giggles]

630
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,800
[wind chimes chiming]

631
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:11,480
♪ Millions of celestial warriors
Went into action ♪

632
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:13,040
♪ There's no way
To make me surrender ♪

633
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:15,080
♪ It wasn't you that can
Decide who wins or loses ♪

634
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:17,280
♪ I wreaked havoc
In the Heavenly Kingdom with my bang ♪

635
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:18,200
Sir.

636
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,400
I'm really lucky to have met you.

637
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,160
Don't speak like that.

638
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:25,480
Why are you calling me "sir"?
I'm still young.

639
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,400
Drop the formalities.

640
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,960
-[laughs]
-Try my special drink.

641
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:30,520
[Qiao Chen] Okay.

642
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:34,320
Mm! Hey.

643
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,840
What's wrong? Does it taste bad?

644
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,760
[laughs]
Hey.

645
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:41,480
[Qiao Chen] This Chinese style
house is really nice.

646
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:43,400
And you got a tennis court here?

647
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:46,600
I often play tennis with my son.

648
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:49,280
Does your son like playing tennis?

649
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:51,720
Yes, he is not bad.
I will introduce you to each other.

650
00:33:51,800 --> 00:33:53,040
Which school is he in?

651
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:55,160
He's in Yu Qing. Have you heard of it?

652
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,400
He's in the tennis club

653
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:57,800
that I was in before.

654
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,160
Yu Qing?

655
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:02,520
Are you Lu Xiangqian?

656
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:04,080
[giggles]

657
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:06,600
You recognized me.
I didn't change much, right?

658
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:09,320
Is your son named Lu Xia?

659
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,080
Yes. Do you know him?

660
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:15,239
[sighs]
I always take care of him at school.

661
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:19,520
His skill improved very fast
after meeting me.

662
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:20,639
Really?

663
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:25,360
Being friends with me gave him
a perfect school life.

664
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,920
I am so relieved to hear that.

665
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:31,600
-[exhales deeply]
-I will let you take care of my son, boy.

666
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:34,199
[calm music]

667
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:45,400
Lu Xia.

668
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:53,520
This is your uniform.

669
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,280
Thanks.

670
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,920
What?

671
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,360
Uh...

672
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,480
Nothing.

673
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:16,680
I just thought it was awesome.

674
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,080
Awesome?

675
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:20,880
You mean the uniform?

676
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:25,440
Could you try it on?
I would like to see it.

677
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:27,200
I would wear it in the game.

678
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,440
Uh, okay.

679
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:32,880
You are right.

680
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,480
Sorry.

681
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,680
[Lu Xia] It fits me well.

682
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,200
[Ying gasps]

683
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,440
[chuckles]

684
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:01,160
I just want to say...

685
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:04,160
Congratulations on being
on the first team.

686
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,880
Thanks.

687
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:16,800
YU QING

688
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:19,960
-[teacher] Stand up.
-[all] Goodbye, teacher.

689
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,240
[woman 2] Please help me review.

690
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:24,520
I didn't get it.

691
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:29,000
[Siyang] Our first opponent
is Yu Hang High School.

692
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:33,760
[Coach Qi] It's our first game
against another school.

693
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,480
We have to make a new training plan.

694
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:38,120
Yes, the competition is really fierce.

695
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:41,640
Only the top two
can participate in the nationals.

696
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:43,080
[inhales sharply]

697
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:44,880
Who do you think
can be in the third singles?

698
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,680
Qiao Chen or Lu Xia?

699
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:48,760
It doesn't matter.

700
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:51,680
As long as we have Yu Qing Tennis Club,
I am confident.

701
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,720
Mm.

702
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,800
[Coach Qi exhales sharply]

703
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:58,200
REGIONALS COMPETITION SCHEDULE

704
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,760
[tense music]

705
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:09,480
It's men's business,
let the skills speak for you.

706
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:11,200
It's a do or die.

707
00:37:11,680 --> 00:37:14,160
The loser will give up the third singles.

708
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:15,400
No problem.

709
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,440
[man 1] The rain has stopped.
Let's continue.

710
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:24,680
I have extra tutoring tonight.

711
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:25,680
[man 2] Okay.

712
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,400
[both grunting]

713
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,800
[suspenseful music]

714
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:47,320
This is a good place.

715
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,280
Yes. It's not that bad.

716
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,880
Excuse me. Do we have to pay to play?

717
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,280
It's free.

718
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:56,720
Are you new here?

719
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,080
Yes.

720
00:37:58,360 --> 00:38:00,840
It is free,
but this is the only court around.

721
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:03,800
Do you know the rules?

722
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,440
I don't know.

723
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:09,560
They are asking and responding in chorus.

724
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,320
It's so annoying.

725
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:14,400
It's simple. We'll challenge you.

726
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:16,040
We'll play a game of four points.

727
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:18,560
You have to leave the court if you lose.

728
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,400
Fine, no problem.

729
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,560
I'll go first.

730
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,120
I will never leave the court.

731
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,480
-I'll go first.
-Why are you guys fighting?

732
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:28,960
Can't you see?

733
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:30,840
We only play doubles here.

734
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:40,120
We are here to play singles
with each other, right?

735
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,480
Is there any other way?
We're already here.

736
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,440
We have to win to talk to them.

737
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:47,440
A high school student
and a middle school student.

738
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:49,240
What a special couple.

739
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:53,040
What are they talking about?

740
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,920
-They think you are in middle school.
-What?

741
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:58,840
Fine.

742
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:00,800
Let's teach them a lesson.

743
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,240
Hm.

744
00:39:08,640 --> 00:39:10,280
[grunting]

745
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,560
[yells]

746
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:22,680
[man 3 groans]

747
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,360
Who will go next?

748
00:39:28,640 --> 00:39:29,800
Seems that no one is around.

749
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:31,840
Then we can have a good game.

750
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:34,480
[man 2] Who said nobody's around?

751
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:36,560
[tense music]

752
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:52,200
They are inexperienced in doubles.

753
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:54,000
[man 2 scoffs]
I can see that.

754
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,800
Bring it on.

755
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,480
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

756
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,200
That one was mine.

757
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:26,040
Don't you understand?

758
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,600
[Qiao Chen] You don't understand at all.

759
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:30,800
-Hm?
-[man 2 scoffs]

760
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:32,000
[snickers]

761
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,600
[bird cawing]

762
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:42,520
Why didn't you get the ball?

763
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:44,480
Didn't you want to get it?

764
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:48,080
[sighs]

765
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:52,480
[grunts]

766
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:55,080
[thwacking]

767
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,560
Lu Xia.

768
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:03,480
Hit the ball.

769
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:08,680
[Lu Xia] I thought that one was out.

770
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:13,480
It's my first time playing doubles.

771
00:41:13,560 --> 00:41:16,440
I forgot that there is no outside
in doubles.

772
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,920
You've never played doubles before?

773
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,680
What do you think?

774
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:27,960
They are terrible.

775
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:30,880
[scoffs]

776
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:32,440
Leave. Next.

777
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:34,600
You just don't cooperate.

778
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,080
What made you say that?

779
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:40,680
I won't lose if we play singles.

780
00:41:42,560 --> 00:41:45,480
Whoa! You two surely
are the top doubles pair of Yu Hang.

781
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:48,480
-[man 2] They are just two idiots.
-[man 1] Yes.

782
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:51,920
How could you compare them to us?

783
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:55,280
[scoffs]
They are good at singles.

784
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:56,920
But as for doubles,

785
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,520
they are like babies.

786
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:00,840
-[men laugh]
-Yu Hang High School.

787
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,840
BU ZHONGCHUAN,
YU HANG HIGH SCHOOL

788
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,840
WU QUAN,
YU HANG HIGH SCHOOL

789
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:06,560
They will be our opponents.

790
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,400
[Lu Xia sighs]

791
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:14,000
Qiao Chen, I thought it through.

792
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,760
I'll give up competing
for the third single.

793
00:42:18,680 --> 00:42:20,680
[closing theme music]

794
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:30,400
♪ The childlike face
Is changing little by little ♪

795
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:32,960
♪ Destiny gives me callused hands ♪

796
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:38,480
♪ On the playground,
We hang on and practice once more ♪

797
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:44,960
♪ We vow with a high five on the court ♪

798
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:48,800
♪ A bunch of youth
