799
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:53,760
♪ The air is filled with cheers ♪

800
00:42:55,440 --> 00:43:01,560
♪ I want to have
An impressive performance ♪

801
00:43:01,640 --> 00:43:03,360
♪ An impressive performance ♪

802
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:09,840
♪ I will never be tired
Of standing by your side ♪

803
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:13,560
♪ Sweating for our dreams ♪

804
00:43:13,640 --> 00:43:15,440
♪ The splendor of growing up ♪

805
00:43:15,520 --> 00:43:19,160
♪ Fight with the rackets,
